rence each time. driving me nuts", "channel": "C_FRONTEND", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 4, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1771618080.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "fae2eb4f59ef58078d22ad6fee9e6730", "ts": "1771946100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_CREEVES", "text": "Hey, got four more tickets for you this sprint. Need these wrapped by Friday.\n- BRIGHT-340: product card hover states on mobile\n- BRIGHT-341: blog font-size inconsistency between sections\n- BRIGHT-342: modal overlay not dimming on firefox\n- BRIGHT-343: contact form layout breaks below 480px", "channel": "D_RC", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "ea030f9b8d1d54329b8cf1241d274ba4", "ts": "1771946280.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RWILSON", "text": "4 more? i already have 328, 330, and 331 this sprint", "channel": "D_RC", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "6b5e82f4b51f5a5c8bd4e8a5a880f46b", "ts": "1771946400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_CREEVES", "text": "yeah i know it's a lot. marketing launch is this weekend, site needs to be clean. you're the fastest on this stuff", "channel": "D_RC", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "2cb9ead9ad655870b80d1b174bb5bde5", "ts": "1771946520.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RWILSON", "text": "ok i'll make it work", "channel": "D_RC", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], 